      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAINTED BEAUTY (4) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 3.5 lengths third (22.66) over 400m at this track. Sure to be about the mark. FANTASIA SHINE (1) was game in defeat at the latest run, finishing second and beaten a neck (26.74) behind Karoline Banner at this track. The form out of his last race has been franked. Will give a great sight again. AL'S MEMORY (3) has been in the placings at his last two runs, most recently when third (24.95) in a Mix over 440m at Goulburn. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. INDY'S SHINE (2) can run a bold race on best form.",
